---
// Introduction page component for the encounter tables document
---

<div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center h-[287mm] p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-green-50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl w-full space-y-4">
    
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div class="text-center space-y-4">
      <h1 class="font-pixeloperator text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
        Wild Pokémon Encounter Tables
      </h1>
      <h2 class="font-pixeloperator text-xl text-gray-600">
        Comprehensive Guide to Wild Pokémon
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Description Section -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-2 border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="font-pixeloperator text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        About This Document
      </h3>
      <div class="font-pixeloperator text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-3 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          This document provides complete encounter tables for wild Pokemon avaialble in the game. 
          Each location is documented with detailed information about which Pokémon can be found, 
          their encounter rates, and the level ranges you can expect to encounter them at.
        </p>
        <p>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Fishing Rod Color Coding Section -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-2 border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="font-pixeloperator text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        Fishing Encounter Color Guide
      </h3>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="font-pixeloperator text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Fishing encounters are color-coded by the type of fishing rod required:
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <!-- Old Rod -->
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-3 bg-teal-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-teal-500">
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-teal-500 rounded"></div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-pixeloperator font-bold text-teal-700">Old Rod</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Good Rod -->
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500">
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-blue-500 rounded"></div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-pixeloperator font-bold text-blue-700">Good Rod</span>

            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Super Rod -->
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-purple-500">
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-purple-500 rounded"></div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-pixeloperator font-bold text-purple-700">Super Rod</span>
 
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- How to Use Section -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-2 border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="font-pixeloperator text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        How to Use This Guide
      </h3>
      <div class="font-pixeloperator text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Each location shows encounter tables for different methods (Land, Surf, Fishing, Rock Smash)</li>
          <li>Level ranges indicate the minimum and maximum levels you can encounter each Pokémon</li>
          <li>Encounter rates show the percentage chance of finding each Pokémon</li>
          <li>Colored bars in fishing tables indicate which fishing rod is required</li>
          <li>Empty sections mean no Pokémon are available via that method in that location</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Team Note Section -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-100 to-teal-100 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-2 border-emerald-300">
      <div class="text-center space-y-3">
        <div class="font-pixeloperator text-sm text-justify text-emerald-700 space-y-2">
            This document has been carefully compiled from the source code to ensure accuracy. Please report any errors if you find them.
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1">
          <p class="text-xs text-emerald-600">
            — The Emerald Imperium Team
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
